  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/javascriptcore\/c-javascriptcore-api\ncrawled: 2026-03-10T17:05:20Z\n---\n\n# C JavaScriptCore API\n\n**API Collection**\n\nBrowse the alternative C-based APIs for JavaScriptCore.\n\n## JavaScriptCore Engine Interface\n\n- **JSContextGroupRef**: A group that associates JavaScript contexts with one another.\n- **JSContextRef**: A JavaScript execution context.\n- **JSGlobalContextRef**: A global JavaScript execution context.\n- **JSStringRef**: A UTF-16 character buffer.\n- **JSClassRef**: A JavaScript class.\n\n## JavaScript Data Types\n\n- **JSValueRef**: A JavaScript value.\n- **JSObjectRef**: A JavaScript object.\n\n## Script Evaluation\n\n- **JSCheckScriptSyntax(_:_:_:_:_:)**: Checks for syntax errors in a string of JavaScript.\n- **JSEvaluateScript(_:_:_:_:_:_:)**: Evaluates a string of JavaScript.\n- **JSGarbageCollect(_:)**: Performs a JavaScript garbage collection.\n\n## Constants\n\n- **JSC_OBJC_API_ENABLED**\n\n",
